"title": "4111: angels, as God's servants",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4111",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Angels have specific yet limited roles to play in declaring God's will and purposes for humanity.</p>\n<h2>Angels are God's servants</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:20\">PSA 103:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:7\">HEB 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:4\">PSA 104:4</a></p>\n<h3>Named angels</h3>\n<p>The archangel Michael:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:13\">DAN 10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:1\">DAN 12:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:9\">JUD 1:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev12:7\">REV 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:16\">DAN 8:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:21\">DAN 9:21</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:19\">LUK 1:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:26\">LUK 1:26</a></p>\n<h2>Angels as agents of God's salvation</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:14\">HEB 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:23\">EXO 23:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod32:34\">EXO 32:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:2\">EXO 33:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:16\">NUM 20:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:8-Isa63:9\">ISA 63:8–63:9</a></p>\n<h3>Angels do not fully understand God's salvation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:10-1Pet1:12\">1PE 1:10–1:12</a></p>\n<h3>Angels deliver God's people from their enemies</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:35\">2KI 19:35</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:21\">2CH 32:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:36\">ISA 37:36</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:19\">ACT 5:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:6-Acts12:11\">ACT 12:6–12:11</a></p>\n<h2>Angels as mediators</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:53\">ACT 7:53</a></strong> <em>The law was mediated by angels to Moses and Israel</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job33:22-Job33:26\">JOB 33:22–33:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:38\">ACT 7:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:19\">GAL 3:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:2\">HEB 2:2</a></p>\n<h2>Angels as revealers of God's will</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech1:8-Zech1:10\">ZEC 1:8–1:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:15-Dan7:16\">DAN 7:15–7:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech4:11-Zech4:14\">ZEC 4:11–4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:1\">REV 17:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:9\">REV 21:9</a></p>\n<h3>Angels convey and fulfil God's instructions</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:4\">ZEC 3:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:21-Num22:35\">NUM 22:21–22:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:6-Zech3:7\">ZEC 3:6–3:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:13\">MAT 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:8\">GAL 1:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:2\">REV 7:2</a></p>\n<h2>Angels attend to the needs of God's people</h2>\n<h3>Angels provide food at special times</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs19:5-1Kgs19:7\">1KI 19:5–19:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:23-Ps78:25\">PSA 78:23–78:25</a></p>\n<h3>Angels provide protection</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:11-Ps91:12\">PSA 91:11–91:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:15\">GEN 19:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:16\">GEN 48:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:7\">PSA 34:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan3:28\">DAN 3:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:22\">DAN 6:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:10\">MAT 18:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:23-Acts27:24\">ACT 27:23–27:24</a></p>\n<h2>Angels give guidance</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:20\">EXO 23:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:7\">GEN 24:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:40\">GEN 24:40</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:26\">ACT 8:26</a></p>\n<h2>Angels serve Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Angels care for Jesus Christ's needs</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:11\">MAT 4:11</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:13\">MRK 1:13</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:43\">LUK 22:43</a></p>\n<h3>Angels are ready to protect Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:53\">MAT 26:53</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:13\">MAT 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:19-Matt2:20\">MAT 2:19–2:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:6\">MAT 4:6</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:10\">LUK 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:11-Ps91:12\">PSA 91:11–91:12</a></p>\n<h3>Angels are inferior to Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:5-Heb1:13\">HEB 1:5–1:13</a></strong></p>",
